suburban Saint
Louis this afternoon, and made a
stop at the

01:15.609 --> 01:17.144 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
cemetery.

01:17.177 --> 01:19.880 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He got a firsthand look at some
of the damage
and briefly joined the cleanup.

01:19.913 --> 01:25.752 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MIKE PENCE, Vice President of
the United States:
There is no place in America for
hatred or

01:25.786 --> 01:27.554 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
acts of prejudice or violence or
anti-Semitism.

01:27.587 --> 01:37.564 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
