Missouri are
inspiring the nation by your
love and care

01:37.597 --> 01:42.836 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
for this place, for the Jewish
community in
Missouri, and I want to thank
you for that

01:42.869 --> 01:47.107 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
