02:40.761 --> 02:44.664 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Jonathan Rugman of Independent
Television
News reports on South Sudan,
where civil war

02:44.698 --> 02:46.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
has brought on disaster.

02:46.466 --> 02:54.007 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
