we will carry
on fighting the war.

03:49.863 --> 03:54.468 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JONATHAN RUGMAN: But confronted
with this
suffering, doing nothing is not
an option,

03:54.501 --> 04:00.207 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and for those arguing that aid
needs to be
tied to political reform, what
an appalling

04:00.240 --> 04:02.042 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
