05:57.090 --> 06:04.898 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Let's turn our
focus out
West to Northern California,
where rain and

06:04.931 --> 06:08.768 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
