once-drought-stricken
region.

06:08.802 --> 06:12.739 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Officials in San Jose ordered
some 14,000
people to evacuate overnight.

06:12.772 --> 06:16.576 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Floodwaters did stabilize today,
but neighborhoods
were inundated.

06:16.610 --> 06:21.815 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Officials said they don't yet
know when residents
will be able to return to their
homes.

06:21.848 --> 06:24.517 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We're now joined by the mayor of
San Jose,
Sam Liccardo.

06:24.551 --> 06:26.419 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Mayor Liccardo, I just want to
ask.

06:26.453 --> 06:31.725 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
You have got 14,000 out for
sure, another
20,000 encouraged to leave.

06:31.758 --> 06:35.595 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
All of them want this
information that you
can't give them yet, which is,
when will they

06:35.629 --> 06:37.364 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
be able to go back home?

06:37.397 --> 06:39.866 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
®MD-BO /SAM LICCARDO, Mayor of
San Jose,
California: Yes, the important
message is

06:39.899 --> 06:41.668 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
that we're not out of this yet.

06:41.701 --> 06:45.038 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Although the waters are
receding, we know
we have got other storms that
are coming in.

06:45.071 --> 06:47.941 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And it's not safe to go in many
of these neighborhoods
yet.

06:47.974 --> 06:50.777 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
We have got a lot of very
contaminated water.

06:50.810 --> 06:53.213 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And we don't want folks going in
there if
they're going to be in peril.

06:53.246 --> 06:56.916 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Do you have
any estimate
on how significant the damage
is?

06:56.950 --> 06:59.286 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
SAM LICCARDO: Not yet.

06:59.319 --> 07:03.590 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Right now, we're really just
focused on making
sure we're taking care of the
families and

07:03.623 --> 07:05.358 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
