opportunity to get
building inspectors in there to
really look

07:08.194 --> 07:10.297 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
at the housing and make sure
it's safe.

07:10.330 --> 07:12.232 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And we will have a better sense
in the days
to come.

07:12.265 --> 07:15.502 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: But why did it
take so long
to evacuate these folks?

07:15.535 --> 07:17.671 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
We were reporting on this in the
East Coast.

07:17.704 --> 07:19.239 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
People knew that this storm was
coming.

07:19.272 --> 07:20.240 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
You knew.

07:20.273 --> 07:22.142 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
You had the weather forecast.

07:22.175 --> 07:25.312 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Yet now we see reports that it
was late last
night where the police were
pounding on doors

07:25.345 --> 07:27.847 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
and saying, hey, come on, it's
too late, you
have got to move.

07:27.881 --> 07:33.987 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SAM LICCARDO: Yes, it's fair to
say we were
preparing for a storm, but what
really flooded

07:34.020 --> 07:41.227 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
these neighborhoods was the
overpouring of
a dam, Anderson Dam, which
released a torrent

07:41.261 --> 07:46.099 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
of water that exceeded our
100-year flood
estimate.

07:46.132 --> 07:51.771 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Essentially, the flood maps, the
data that
we were relying on wasn't
preparing us for

07:51.805 --> 07:53.573 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
this.

07:53.606 --> 07:56.710 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so we are clearly learning
some very hard
lessons here, and we have got a
lot to fix

07:56.743 --> 07:58.511 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
going forward.

07:58.545 --> 08:01.948 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Anderson Dam,
which feeds
that Coyote Creek area, some
engineers say

08:01.981 --> 08:06.653 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
