won't be substantial,
because we need to get some sun
on this reservoir

08:32.512 --> 08:34.314 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
to get some of that water
evaporated.

08:34.347 --> 08:38.451 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Has the city
requested any
sort of aid from the state or
the federal

08:38.485 --> 08:40.320 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
government?

08:40.353 --> 08:43.723 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
SAM LICCARDO: I had a
conversation with the
governor's office just a couple
of hours ago.

08:43.757 --> 08:45.759 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
