great testament
to their hard work.

09:01.574 --> 09:04.711 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But we know we're probably going
to need help
in the weeks to come.

09:04.744 --> 09:07.480 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And we're working now with the
state to figure
out how we can do that.

09:07.514 --> 09:10.016 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: How many
people do you still
have in emergency shelters?

09:10.049 --> 09:11.351 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
