members nearby.

09:25.265 --> 09:30.537 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So we're going to do everything
we can to
help folks who are displaced and
see how we

09:30.570 --> 09:32.372 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
