feet.

09:32.405 --> 09:37.544 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
What's been a remarkable thing
is to see how
the community has reached out in
various ways

09:37.577 --> 09:39.145 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
to help these families.

09:39.179 --> 09:43.316 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
